Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleopatra,\NI can ask it now. Even though your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,says, well, that was a couple thousand\Nyears ago.
