Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.36,1:24:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,not to put your foot in the p cage with\Nthe Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.04,1:24:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're not doing that out of fear.\NYou're doing that out of your awareness
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.36,1:24:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and respect for reality.\NJust like when you drive the car, you
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.32,1:25:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,don't close your eyes at 60 miles an\Nhour down the highway. So that's respect
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.80,1:25:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,for the linear realities of this world.\NThe fears that we're talking about are
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.04,1:25:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,fears of the unknown\Nand other other fears that are not, you
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.40,1:25:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,know, respect for uh physical realities.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.40,1:25:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it isn't out of fear that you don't\Ndrive 60 miles an hour with your eyes
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.60,1:25:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,closed. It's out of respect for the\Nphysical reality of the world, but not
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.92,1:26:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,fear.\NAnd
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.00,1:26:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> and the fear that you are referring to.\NCan you say more on the fear?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.36,1:26:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,>> The it isn't the fear. It's the respect\Nfor the reality. So fear alone won't
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.15,1:26:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,keep you alive in this world.\NFear won't keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.52,1:26:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear won't keep you alive. Respect for\Nreality is what keeps you alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.08,1:26:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So a fear is a poor substitute for a\Nsense of reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.96,1:26:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So when people drink too much,\Nthey lose their sense of reality and
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.23,1:27:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,turn their automobiles over on the\Nhighway.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.23,1:27:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're probably fearless when they\Ndo that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.96,1:27:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So fear is a respect for reality, cause\Nand effect in the linear domain.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.84,1:27:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.12,1:28:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N>> Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.92,1:28:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Many of your students are also\Npracticing the course in miracles.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.40,1:28:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\NDo we need to have any concern that the
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.08,1:28:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,course in miracles at 600 in any way\Ndilutes your teachings on enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.19,1:28:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,at a thousand?\N>> No.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.71,1:28:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And is there a preferred way to blend\Nthe two?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.36,1:28:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Well, you would have to do it in a way\Nthat makes sense to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.28,1:28:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Read the books, practice the course, and\Ndon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.08,1:28:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,>> There you go. Thank you.\Nand and do the 12 steps in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.71,1:28:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,>> What happens now, honey?\N>> We're going to do our goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.40,1:29:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh my god. Okay.\NSo, now we will close the meeting and I
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.84,1:29:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I will walk out in front.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.63,1:29:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have the music to help us close.\NYes, I think we help. That helps us
Dialogue: 0,1:29:15.76,1:29:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,close.\NWho's this? Santa Claus.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.60,1:29:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Dr.\N>> Oh my god. Isn't that something?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.52,1:29:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You are you are God's gift to me\Nfor which I give thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.28,1:29:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks for all all who are\Npresent
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.04,1:30:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because\Nby commitment to the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.44,1:30:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we are together\Nforever.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.80,1:30:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a fact. Resist.\NBy virtue of our commitment,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.63,1:30:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we are karmically aligned.\NThose who are destined to become
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.60,1:30:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightened.\NSo in this room
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.52,1:30:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,are the future spiritual teachers\Nof generations to come. Generations to
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.00,1:30:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,come.\NMy teacher was five or six lifetimes ago
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.71,1:30:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just got around to it now.\NWhat I said is true.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.28,1:30:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Within this room are the great teachers\Nof the future. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.19,1:31:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Within this realm are great teachers of\Nspiritual truth of the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.84,1:31:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Some even at the present already\Nperhaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.48,1:31:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What a divine blessing. What more could\None ask from God?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.63,1:31:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Money comes and goes. Good lucks come\Nand go.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.60,1:31:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Strength comes and goes.\NMoney comes and goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.40,1:31:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual truth is eternal.\NAnd the destiny
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.28,1:31:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of having been a human\Nis eternal salvation.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.32,1:31:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternal.\NSo our destiny is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.28,1:31:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea that we're separate\Ndissolves as an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.19,1:32:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not separate.\NWe're all one.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.48,1:32:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking through a variety of bodies.\NThere is only one here. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.44,1:32:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one\Nin this entire room.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.08,1:32:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the true truth. Resist.\NThere's only one
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.00,1:32:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in this whole room\Npervading the consciousness of all of us
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.19,1:32:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,simultaneously.\NWow,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.88,1:32:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that's exciting.\NI never discovered that before. Thank
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.88,1:32:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you, Lord.\NThat there is only the one and we're it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.40,1:32:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NWe share in it. Yes, we share in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.56,1:33:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.\NThank God for some good karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.08,1:33:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody worries about their bad karma.\NHow long does it take to undo bad karma?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.40,1:33:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How long?\NYeah, I thought that long.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.80,1:33:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's gone.\NThe bad karma has gone in one instant by
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.92,1:33:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,an act of the will.\NBy surrendering to God, by saying glory
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.52,1:33:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to God in the highest,\Nall glory and power is thine, oh Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.84,1:33:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In that one act, you undo all the\Nignorance of past life.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.71,1:33:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is bad karma? Nothing but\Nignorance.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.88,1:33:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ and the Buddha, they all\Nsaid
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.92,1:34:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,all that the world calls negative.\NNothing but ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.08,1:34:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorance.\NThere is no evil. There's only
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.15,1:34:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,ignorance.\NThere's only ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.19,1:34:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To be enlight means to surrender that\Nignorance
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.12,1:34:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,out of humility.\NNot out of desperation, not out of
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.63,1:34:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,wantingness,\Nbut out of humility. You surrender that
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.44,1:34:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,ignorance.\NI myself do not know. Oh Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.15,1:34:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have myself do not know.\NSo we surrender our ignorance and our
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.92,1:35:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,limitation and our not knowingness\Nto God.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.92,1:35:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And in return,\Nwe become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.92,1:35:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,People think enlightenment is way in the\Nfuture and it's way up there. I'll tell
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.19,1:35:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you where enlightenment is. It's right\Nhere. It's right now. It's right here
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.00,1:35:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and right now. This is enlightenment.\NResist.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.80,1:35:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no point to pray about being\Nenlightened in the future. It's right
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.52,1:35:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,here, right now\Nas you
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.08,1:35:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you are it.\NSo you share the joy of that knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.23,1:35:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,with the world,\Nbut you don't tell them.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.32,1:36:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We are what the world has been waiting\Nfor.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.12,1:36:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, doctor.\NPut him away again. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.56,1:36:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. We give thanks that we can be\Nof service to the Lord
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.60,1:36:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,by fulfilling our spiritual potential to\Nthe best that we can.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:25.92,1:36:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to become Buddha. You\Ndon't have to become Jesus. You don't
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.19,1:36:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,have to become Krishna.\NYou acknowledge their presence already
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.67,1:36:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,within you.\NKrishna, Buddha, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.88,1:36:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ is within all of us now.\NResist. It's within all of us now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.15,1:37:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do we acknowledge it?\NBy giving thanks for it. Lord God, I
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.96,1:37:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,give thanks.\NThat divine presence
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.63,1:37:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,expressed as all of us here at this\Nmoment.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.40,1:37:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And in this moment, we love each other\Neternally.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.71,1:37:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.\NWhy is that? Because we cannot be any
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.08,1:37:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,other way.\NYou can't say I think I love this one
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.28,1:37:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and this one and not this one and then\Nthis one. You either love everybody or
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.40,1:37:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't love anybody.\NNow, everyone here has already
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.15,1:37:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,moved into an incredible state of\Nconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.19,1:38:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We serve God by being that which we are\Nto the fullest
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.48,1:38:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to love everything to the fullest that\Nwe can to see the intrinsic beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.67,1:38:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in the Kimod dragon, he he goes the\Nway he goes because that's the only way
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.56,1:38:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,he knows how to be.\NSo you can't just restrict it to cute
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.44,1:38:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,doggies.\NBut everything that lives,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.92,1:38:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,all the world as it is,\Nwhen you love it unre unreservedly,
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.88,1:38:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that creation is divinity.\NCreation and divinity are one in the
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.32,1:38:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,same thing.\NSo you live in the presence of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.19,1:38:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You live all the time in the presence of\Ndivinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.40,1:38:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in waiting till we'll\Nwait till after I die and then I'll go
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.08,1:39:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to heaven and then we'll worship God.\NIf you can't worship God here and now,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.63,1:39:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not going to worship God in\Nheaven. You're just going to wander
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.84,1:39:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,around in your atheric body having a\Ngood time flirting with the other
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.36,1:39:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,bodies.\NI've been in it. I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.96,1:39:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, your commitment here and now is what\Nwill prevail when you leave the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.08,1:39:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you really are then prevails.\NSo our love for each other is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:33.44,1:39:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Our love for Dr. Moon,\Nfor all our visitors from Korea, by whom
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.80,1:39:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we are whose presence we are blessed\Nthis day and for whom we give thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.71,1:40:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We can all hum to the music.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.60,1:41:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NYes,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.96,1:41:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.71,1:42:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.36,1:42:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.36,1:43:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelu
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.67,1:43:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.11,1:43:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.04,1:44:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:17.36,1:44:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NOkay, that's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.32,1:44:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not against the law to hug the\Nperson next to you. God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.60,1:45:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I see you next time. Amen.\N>> How about one?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.92,1:45:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I know.\N>> I use the M to get me off the singing
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.92,1:45:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I need something to get me off\Nthe
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.76,1:45:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God bless everyone here. Amen.\N>> Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.63,1:45:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelu
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.44,1:46:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelu
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.15,1:46:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.
